import Layout from "../components/Layout/Layout";
import { Flex } from "../components/Flex/Flex";
import Box from "../components/Box/Box";
import { Title } from "../components/Title/Title";
import { Text } from "../components/Text/Text";
import { ButtonPrimary } from "../components/Button/Button";

const Index = () => (
  <Layout>
    <Flex
      mt={165}
      w={1}
      border="1px solid red"
      alignItems="center"
      justifyContent="center"
      flexDirection="column"
    >
      <Flex
        w={1}
        border="1px solid red"
        alignItems="stretch"
        justifyContent="space-between"
      >
        <Flex
          maxWidth={500}
          flexDirection="column"
          alignItems="flex-start"
          border="1px solid"
        >
          <Title fontFamily="Georgia" fontSize={65} mb={55} color="#151515">
            Trabalhar remoto nunca foi tão produtivo!
          </Title>
          <Text fontSize={24} mb={55}>
            Gerencie o tempo do seu time, orquetre as tarefas, automatize
            processos e muito mais.
          </Text>
          <ButtonPrimary>EXPERIMENTE GRÁTIS</ButtonPrimary>
        </Flex>
        <Flex border="1px solid red">testetsteteteeeeeeeetttttttttttttt</Flex>
      </Flex>
      <Flex maxWidth={500} alignItems="center" flexDirection="column">
        <Flex>
          <Title>Organize tudo por áreas e projetos</Title>
          <Text>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec
            euismod egestas porta. Nulla facilisi. Phasellus tristique in est at
            maximus. Nullam dignissim tellus quis ipsum lacinia vestibulum.
          </Text>
        </Flex>
      </Flex>
    </Flex>
  </Layout>
);

export default Index;
